title: iPhone 14 Pro CAD renders showcase its unique dual hole-punch cutouts
content:
Apple might finally be ready to ditch the dreaded notch this year. As per recent reports, the company is planning to replace the notch on the upcoming iPhone 14 Pro and iPhone 14 Pro Max with a unique hole+pill cutout solution. A new set of CAD renders of the iPhone 14 Pro confirm this new

The post iPhone 14 Pro CAD renders showcase its unique dual hole-punch cutouts appeared first on xda-developers.
description: Leaked CAD renders of the upcoming iPhone 14 Pro suggest that Apple could finally ditch the notch this year. Read on to learn more.
